properties.description: 自然语言处理（Natural Language Processing, NLP）是人工智能和语言学的一个分支领域，致力于研究计算机与人类语言之间的交互，使计算机能够理解、解释、生成和操纵自然语言文本或语音。

properties.name: 文本分类
properties.description: 自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在将文本按照预定义的类别进行自动分类

properties.name: 命名实体识别
properties.description: 自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在识别文本中具有特定意义的命名实体，如人名、地名、机构名等，并将其分类到预定义的类别中。

properties.name: 机器翻译
properties.description: 机器翻译是自然语言处理的一个子领域，专注于利用计算机自动将一种自然语言翻译成另一种自然语言的技术。

properties.name: 情感分析
properties.description: 自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在识别、提取和量化文本中的主观信息，如情绪、观点和态度

properties.name: 问答系统
properties.description: 问答系统是自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在通过计算机自动回答用户提出的问题。

properties.name: 文本摘要
properties.description: 自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在从文本中提取或生成简洁且包含关键信息的摘要。

properties.name: 语义分析
properties.description: 语义分析是自然语言处理的一个子领域，主要研究如何理解和解释文本或语音中的意义，包括词义、句义和篇章义的分析。

properties.name: 信息抽取
properties.description: 信息抽取是自然语言处理的一个子领域，旨在从非结构化或半结构化文本中自动识别并提取特定类型的信息，如实体、关系、事件等。

properties.name: 词性标注
properties.description: 自然语言处理中的一项基础任务，旨在为文本中的每个词汇或符号分配一个特定的词性标签（如名词、动词、形容词等）

properties.name: 语音识别
properties.description: 将人类语音转换为文本或命令的技术
properties.applications: 智能助手、语音转写、语音控制、实时字幕

properties.name: 句法分析
properties.description: 句法分析是自然语言处理中的一项基础任务，旨在分析句子的语法结构，确定词语之间的依存关系或短语结构。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、信息抽取、问答系统、文本摘要

properties.name: 语义角色标注
properties.description: 语义角色标注是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在识别句子中谓词与其相关的语义角色，如施事、受事、时间、地点等。
properties.applications: 信息抽取、问答系统、机器翻译、文本理解

properties.name: 主题分类
properties.description: 一种文本分类任务，旨在根据文本内容将其分配到一个或多个预定义的主题类别中。
properties.applications: 新闻分类、内容推荐、信息检索、社交媒体分析

properties.name: 垃圾邮件检测
properties.description: 识别和过滤不需要的、通常是商业性质的电子邮件，以防止其进入用户的收件箱
properties.applications: 电子邮件服务、网络安全、用户隐私保护

properties.name: 意图识别
properties.description: 识别用户输入文本背后的意图或目的，通常用于对话系统和虚拟助手。
properties.applications: 聊天机器人、智能客服、语音助手、自动问答系统

properties.name: 朴素贝叶斯
properties.description: 一种基于贝叶斯定理的简单概率分类器，假设特征之间相互独立，常用于文本分类等自然语言处理任务。

properties.name: 支持向量机
properties.description: 一种基于统计学习理论的监督学习算法，用于分类和回归分析，通过寻找最优超平面来实现数据分类。

properties.name: 逻辑回归
properties.description: 逻辑回归是一种用于解决二分类问题的统计方法，通过逻辑函数将线性回归的输出映射到0和1之间，用于预测概率。

properties.name: 随机森林
properties.description: 随机森林是一种集成学习方法，通过构建多个决策树并结合它们的预测结果来提高模型的准确性和鲁棒性。

properties.name: 卷积神经网络
properties.description: 一种深度学习模型，通过卷积层自动提取局部特征，广泛应用于图像识别、文本分类等领域

properties.name: 循环神经网络
properties.description: 一种用于处理序列数据的神经网络结构，通过循环连接实现对历史信息的记忆和处理，广泛应用于自然语言处理、语音识别等领域。

properties.name: Transformer
properties.description: A deep learning model architecture based on self-attention mechanisms, primarily used in natural language processing tasks.

properties.name: 命名实体识别与分类
properties.description: 识别文本中的命名实体（如人名、地名、组织名等）并将其分类到预定义的类别中
properties.applications: 信息提取、问答系统、机器翻译、知识图谱构建

properties.name: 嵌套命名实体识别
properties.description: 一种识别文本中嵌套命名实体的自然语言处理任务，即识别并分类文本中相互包含的命名实体。
properties.applications: 信息提取、问答系统、知识图谱构建

properties.name: 跨语言命名实体识别
properties.description: 跨语言命名实体识别是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在从不同语言的文本中识别和分类命名实体（如人名、地名、组织名等）。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、跨语言信息检索、多语言知识图谱构建

properties.name: 细粒度命名实体识别
properties.description: 细粒度命名实体识别是命名实体识别的一个子任务，旨在识别和分类文本中更具体、更细粒度的实体类型，如药品名称、疾病名称、特定品牌等，而不仅仅是传统的人名、地名和组织名。
properties.applications: 信息抽取、知识图谱构建、医疗文本分析、金融领域实体识别

properties.name: 开放域命名实体识别
properties.description: 开放域命名实体识别是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在从非结构化文本中识别和分类不属于预定义类别的命名实体。
properties.applications: 信息提取、知识图谱构建、问答系统、文本摘要

properties.name: 条件随机场
properties.description: 条件随机场（Conditional Random Field, CRF）是一种用于标注和分割序列数据的统计建模方法，常用于自然语言处理中的序列标注任务，如命名实体识别、词性标注等。

properties.name: 隐马尔可夫模型
properties.description: 隐马尔可夫模型是一种统计模型，用于描述一个含有隐含未知参数的马尔可夫过程。其难点是从可观察的参数中确定该过程的隐含参数，然后利用这些参数来作进一步的分析。

properties.name: 深度学习
properties.description: 一种基于人工神经网络的机器学习方法，能够通过多层次的非线性变换对数据进行高层抽象和模式识别。

properties.name: 规则匹配
properties.description: 一种基于预定义规则的模式匹配技术，用于识别文本中的特定模式或结构

properties.name: 统计机器翻译
properties.description: 一种基于统计模型的机器翻译方法，通过分析大量双语语料库中的统计规律来实现自动翻译。
properties.applications: 跨语言信息检索、多语言文档处理、实时翻译系统

properties.name: 神经机器翻译
properties.description: 神经机器翻译是一种利用神经网络模型进行自动翻译的自然语言处理任务，通过端到端的学习方式将源语言文本转换为目标语言文本。
properties.applications: 跨语言交流、全球化业务、多语言内容生成、实时翻译系统

properties.name: 基于规则的机器翻译
properties.description: 一种机器翻译方法，依赖于预定义的语言规则和词典来将源语言文本转换为目标语言文本。
properties.applications: 专业文档翻译、术语标准化、早期机器翻译系统

properties.name: 多语言机器翻译
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，旨在实现多种语言之间的自动翻译，无需中间语言转换。
properties.applications: 跨语言交流、全球化商业、多语言内容管理、国际会议实时翻译

properties.name: 实时机器翻译
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，旨在实现源语言到目标语言的即时自动翻译，通常要求在毫秒级延迟内完成。

properties.name: 领域自适应机器翻译
properties.description: 一种机器翻译任务，旨在将翻译模型适应到特定领域，以提高在该领域的翻译质量。
properties.applications: 专业文档翻译、医疗领域翻译、法律文件翻译、技术手册翻译

properties.name: 低资源机器翻译
properties.description: 低资源机器翻译是指在数据稀缺或计算资源有限的情况下进行机器翻译的任务，通常涉及小语种或特定领域的翻译。
properties.applications: 跨语言信息检索、多语言内容生成、小语种翻译支持

properties.name: 基于实例的机器翻译
properties.description: 一种机器翻译方法，通过存储和检索翻译实例库中的双语对照句子或短语来生成翻译结果，无需显式的语法或语义分析。

properties.name: 混合机器翻译
properties.description: 一种结合多种机器翻译方法（如统计机器翻译和神经机器翻译）的技术，旨在利用不同方法的优势以提高翻译质量和准确性。

properties.name: 情感分类
properties.description: 情感分类是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在将文本中的情感倾向分为预定义的类别，如正面、负面或中性。
properties.applications: 产品评论分析、社交媒体监控、客户反馈分析、市场研究

properties.name: 情感极性分析
properties.description: 情感极性分析是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在确定文本中表达的情感是正面、负面还是中性。

properties.name: 情感强度检测
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，旨在识别和量化文本中表达的情感强度，通常用于分析情感的强烈程度而不仅仅是情感极性。
properties.applications: 社交媒体分析、产品评论评估、市场调研、舆情监控

properties.name: 方面级情感分析
properties.description: 一种细粒度的情感分析任务，旨在识别文本中特定方面或实体的情感倾向，而不仅仅是对整个文本进行情感分类。
properties.applications: 产品评论分析、社交媒体监控、客户反馈分析

properties.name: 多模态情感分析
properties.description: 多模态情感分析是一种结合文本、语音、图像等多种模态数据进行情感分析的自然语言处理任务，旨在更全面地理解和识别情感状态。
properties.applications: 社交媒体分析、人机交互、市场调研、心理健康监测

properties.name: 词典匹配
properties.description: 一种基于预定义词典进行文本情感分析的技术方法，通过匹配文本中的词汇与词典中的情感词及其情感极性来计算整体情感倾向。

properties.name: 机器学习方法
properties.description: 用于从数据中学习模式和关系的算法和技术，广泛应用于自然语言处理中的情感分析等任务。

properties.name: 深度学习模型
properties.description: 一种通过多层神经网络进行特征学习和模式识别的机器学习方法，广泛应用于自然语言处理、计算机视觉等领域。

properties.name: 情感词典构建
properties.description: 一种通过构建包含情感极性词汇的词典来进行情感分析的技术方法

properties.name: 情感强度分析
properties.description: 一种用于量化文本中表达的情感强度或极性程度的技术，通常作为情感分析的子任务

properties.name: 阅读理解式问答
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，要求系统通过阅读给定的文本段落来回答相关问题，理解文本的深层含义和上下文关系。
properties.applications: 智能客服、教育辅助、信息检索、知识管理

properties.name: 知识库问答
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，旨在通过查询结构化或半结构化的知识库来回答用户的问题。
properties.applications: 智能客服、医疗诊断辅助、教育问答系统、企业知识管理

properties.name: 社区问答
properties.description: 从社区论坛或问答平台中自动提取和回答用户提出的问题，通常涉及非结构化文本和多样化的语言表达。
properties.applications: 在线客服系统、知识库构建、社区内容管理

properties.name: 开放域问答
properties.description: 开放域问答是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在回答用户提出的任何问题，而不受限于特定领域或主题。
properties.applications: 智能助手、搜索引擎、客户支持系统、教育工具

properties.name: 事实型问答
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理任务，旨在从给定的文本或知识库中提取事实性问题的答案。
properties.applications: 搜索引擎、智能助手、客户支持系统

properties.name: 多跳问答
properties.description: 多跳问答是一种需要多个推理步骤才能回答问题的自然语言处理任务，通常涉及多个文档或信息源的整合。
properties.applications: 智能助手、信息检索、知识图谱问答

properties.name: 阅读理解
properties.description: 一种自然语言处理技术，旨在通过理解和分析文本内容来回答相关问题或提取关键信息。

properties.name: 知识图谱
properties.description: 一种用于表示和存储知识的结构化技术，通过实体、关系和属性来组织和连接信息，支持知识推理和信息检索。

properties.name: 语义解析
properties.description: 语义解析是一种将自然语言句子转换为机器可理解的逻辑形式或结构化查询的技术，常用于问答系统和数据库查询等场景。

properties.name: 对话管理
properties.description: 对话管理是一种在自然语言处理中用于控制对话流程和状态的技术，通常应用于问答系统和聊天机器人中，以确保对话的连贯性和上下文相关性。

properties.name: 单文档摘要
properties.description: 从单个文档中提取关键信息并生成简洁的摘要，保留原文的主要内容和意义。
properties.applications: 新闻摘要、报告生成、信息检索、内容预览

properties.name: 多文档摘要
properties.description: 多文档摘要是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在从多个相关文档中提取关键信息并生成一个简洁、连贯的摘要。
properties.applications: 新闻摘要、法律文档分析、医疗报告生成、商业情报分析

properties.name: 抽取式摘要
properties.description: 一种文本摘要方法，通过从原文中直接抽取重要的句子或短语来生成摘要，保持原文的原始表达。
properties.applications: 新闻摘要、文档摘要、搜索引擎结果摘要

properties.name: 生成式摘要
properties.description: 一种文本摘要方法，通过生成新的句子来概括原文内容，而不是简单提取原文中的句子。
properties.applications: 新闻摘要、报告生成、内容概括、自动文档摘要

properties.name: 标题生成
properties.description: 自动为给定文本生成简洁且具有代表性的标题的NLP任务
properties.applications: 新闻摘要、文档管理、搜索引擎优化、内容推荐系统

properties.name: 关键短语提取
properties.description: 从文本中自动识别和提取最能概括文档主题或内容的关键短语或术语
properties.applications: 信息检索, 文本摘要, 文档分类, 搜索引擎优化

properties.name: 基于图的摘要
properties.description: 一种文本摘要技术，通过构建文本的图表示（如词共现图或依存关系图）并应用图算法（如PageRank）来识别重要内容，生成摘要。

properties.name: 基于神经网络的摘要
properties.description: 一种利用神经网络模型自动生成文本摘要的技术，能够从原始文本中提取关键信息并生成简洁的摘要。

properties.name: 基于注意力的摘要
properties.description: 一种利用注意力机制来识别和提取文本中关键信息的文本摘要技术，能够动态地关注输入文本的不同部分以生成更准确的摘要。

properties.name: 词义消歧
properties.description: 词义消歧是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在根据上下文确定多义词在特定语境中的正确含义。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、信息检索、问答系统、文本摘要

properties.name: 语义相似度计算
properties.description: 衡量两个文本片段在语义上的相似程度，通常用于自然语言处理中的文本匹配、信息检索等任务
properties.applications: 问答系统、机器翻译、文本摘要、信息检索

properties.name: 指代消解
properties.description: 指代消解是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在识别文本中代词或名词短语所指的具体实体，以确定它们之间的指代关系。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、信息抽取、问答系统、文本摘要

properties.name: 实体链接
properties.description: 将文本中提到的实体与知识库中的对应实体进行关联的技术

properties.name: 关系抽取
properties.description: 从文本中识别实体之间的关系，并提取出结构化的关系三元组（实体1，关系，实体2）。
properties.applications: 知识图谱构建、问答系统、信息检索、智能客服

properties.name: 事件抽取
properties.description: 从非结构化文本中识别和提取事件信息，包括事件类型、触发词、参与者、时间、地点等要素
properties.applications: 舆情监控、金融分析、智能客服、知识图谱构建

properties.name: 共指消解
properties.description: 共指消解是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在识别文本中指向同一实体的不同表达，并将其关联起来。
properties.applications: 信息抽取、机器翻译、问答系统、文本摘要

properties.name: 模板填充
properties.description: 一种信息抽取技术，通过预定义的模板从非结构化文本中提取结构化信息

properties.name: 词性消歧
properties.description: 词性消歧是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在根据上下文确定一个词在特定语境中的正确词性。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、信息检索、文本分析

properties.name: 未知词词性标注
properties.description: 对文本中未登录词或罕见词进行词性标注的任务，需要处理词汇表之外的词汇。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、信息抽取、文本分析

properties.name: 跨语言词性标注
properties.description: 跨语言词性标注是一种自然语言处理任务，旨在为不同语言的文本中的词语分配相应的词性标签，通常涉及多语言数据的处理和模型迁移。
properties.applications: 机器翻译、多语言信息提取、跨语言文本分析

properties.name: 最大熵模型
properties.description: 一种基于最大熵原理的概率模型，用于自然语言处理中的序列标注任务，如词性标注。

properties.name: 词错误率
properties.description: 用于衡量语音识别系统性能的指标，计算识别结果与参考文本之间的差异

properties.name: 字错误率
properties.description: 衡量语音识别系统性能的指标，计算识别结果与参考文本之间的字级别差异
properties.range: 0到正无穷，通常以百分比表示，数值越低表示识别准确率越高

properties.name: 准确率
properties.description: 衡量模型预测结果与真实结果一致的比例，常用于分类任务评估

properties.name: LibriSpeech
properties.description: A corpus of approximately 1000 hours of 16kHz read English speech derived from audiobooks, designed for training and evaluating automatic speech recognition systems.

properties.name: Common Voice
properties.description: An open-source dataset of voice recordings contributed by volunteers to help train speech recognition systems.

properties.name: TIMIT
properties.description: A corpus of phonemically and lexically transcribed speech of American English speakers, used for acoustic-phonetic studies and speech recognition system development.

properties.name: VoxCeleb
properties.description: A large-scale speaker identification dataset collected from open-source media, containing over 100,000 utterances from 1,251 celebrities.

properties.name: Switchboard
properties.description: A corpus of spontaneous conversations used for speech recognition research, consisting of telephone conversations between two participants.

properties.name: 召回率
properties.description: 召回率是评估模型正确识别出相关实例的能力的指标，计算为正确识别的相关实例数除以实际相关实例的总数。

properties.name: F1值
properties.description: F1值是精确率和召回率的调和平均数，用于评估分类模型的性能，尤其在数据不平衡的情况下更为有效。

properties.name: 依存准确率
properties.description: 衡量依存句法分析器正确预测句子中词与词之间依存关系的准确率

properties.name: 标记准确率
properties.description: 衡量句法分析中标记预测正确的比例，通常用于评估词性标注或句法标注的准确性

properties.name: Penn Treebank
properties.description: A large annotated corpus of English language text, widely used for training and evaluating natural language processing systems, particularly in syntactic parsing.

properties.name: Chinese Treebank
properties.description: A corpus of annotated Chinese text for syntactic analysis and natural language processing research.

properties.name: Universal Dependencies
properties.description: A framework for consistent annotation of grammar (parts of speech, morphological features, and syntactic dependencies) across different languages.

properties.name: CoNLL-2000
properties.description: A dataset used for shared tasks in computational natural language learning, specifically for chunking tasks in English.

properties.name: CoNLL-2009
properties.description: A dataset used for syntactic and semantic dependency parsing, part of the Conference on Computational Natural Language Learning (CoNLL) shared tasks.

properties.name: 精确率
properties.description: 在语义角色标注任务中，精确率是指被正确预测为正例的样本数占所有被预测为正例的样本数的比例。

properties.name: PropBank
properties.description: A corpus annotated with verb arguments and their semantic roles, used for training and evaluating semantic role labeling systems.

properties.name: NomBank
properties.description: A corpus annotated with predicate-argument structures for nominalizations, supporting research in semantic role labeling.

properties.name: FrameNet
properties.description: A lexical database of English that documents the range of semantic and syntactic combinatory possibilities of each word in the corpus, based on annotated examples of actual language use.

properties.name: CoNLL-2005
properties.description: A dataset for semantic role labeling, used in the CoNLL-2005 shared task.

properties.name: 20 Newsgroups
properties.description: A collection of approximately 20,000 newsgroup documents, partitioned across 20 different newsgroups, used for text classification and natural language processing tasks.

properties.name: AG News
properties.description: AG News is a dataset for news article classification, consisting of over 1 million news articles categorized into 4 topics: World, Sports, Business, and Sci/Tech.

properties.name: DBpedia
properties.description: A large-scale, multilingual knowledge base extracted from Wikipedia, used for various natural language processing tasks including text and topic classification.

properties.name: ROC-AUC
properties.description: Receiver Operating Characteristic Area Under the Curve, a performance measurement for classification problems at various threshold settings

properties.name: 误报率
properties.description: 在垃圾邮件检测中，误报率指被错误分类为垃圾邮件的正常邮件所占的比例。

properties.name: Enron-Spam
properties.description: A dataset containing emails from the Enron corpus labeled as spam or ham, commonly used for spam detection research.

properties.name: SpamAssassin
properties.description: An open-source email filtering system designed to identify and filter spam emails using a variety of techniques including text analysis, Bayesian filtering, and network-based tests.

properties.name: Lingspam
properties.description: A dataset for spam email detection, consisting of labeled email messages in English.

properties.name: TREC 2005 Spam Track
properties.description: A dataset used for evaluating spam detection techniques, part of the Text REtrieval Conference (TREC) in 2005.

properties.name: SMS Spam Collection
properties.description: A dataset containing SMS messages labeled as spam or ham (non-spam), commonly used for text classification and spam detection research.

properties.name: ATIS
properties.description: Airline Travel Information System dataset, commonly used for intent recognition and slot filling in natural language processing.

properties.name: SNIPS
properties.description: A dataset for natural language understanding tasks, particularly focused on intent classification and slot filling.

properties.name: CLINC150
properties.description: A dataset for intent classification containing 150 intent classes across 10 domains, designed for out-of-scope prediction in task-oriented dialogue systems.

properties.name: Banking77

properties.name: DSTC2
properties.description: The Second Dialog State Tracking Challenge dataset, used for evaluating dialog state tracking systems in task-oriented dialogues.

properties.name: 语言建模

properties.applications: 机器翻译、语音识别、文本生成、自动补全

properties.name: 文本生成
properties.description: 使用自然语言处理技术生成连贯、有意义的文本内容
properties.applications: 聊天机器人、内容创作、机器翻译、自动摘要

properties.name: CoNLL-2003
properties.description: A widely used dataset for named entity recognition, containing news wire articles with annotations for person, organization, location, and miscellaneous entities.

properties.name: OntoNotes
properties.description: A large-scale, multi-genre, multilingual corpus annotated with syntactic, semantic, and discourse information, widely used for named entity recognition and classification tasks.

properties.name: WikiGold
properties.description: A dataset for named entity recognition and classification, often used in natural language processing tasks.

properties.name: ACE 2005
properties.description: The ACE 2005 dataset is a standard benchmark for named entity recognition and classification, containing annotated text in multiple languages for various entity types.

properties.name: GENIA
properties.description: A corpus for biomedical text mining, specifically designed for the task of named entity recognition and classification in the domain of molecular biology.

properties.name: TAC KBP
properties.description: The TAC Knowledge Base Population (KBP) is a dataset used for evaluating systems that extract and link information about entities from unstructured text to a knowledge base. It focuses on named entity recognition and classification tasks.

properties.name: F1-score
properties.description: A measure of a test's accuracy that considers both precision and recall, calculated as the harmonic mean of precision and recall.

properties.name: Precision
properties.description: A metric that measures the proportion of correctly identified positive instances among all instances predicted as positive, commonly used in nested named entity recognition tasks.

properties.name: Recall
properties.description: A metric that measures the proportion of actual positives that are correctly identified by the model, particularly in the context of nested named entity recognition.

properties.name: Exact Match
properties.description: A strict evaluation metric that requires the predicted named entity to exactly match the ground truth in both boundary and type to be considered correct.

properties.name: Overlap-based Metrics
properties.description: Metrics used to evaluate the performance of nested named entity recognition systems by measuring the overlap between predicted and actual entity spans.

properties.name: CoNLL 2003
properties.description: A dataset for named entity recognition, commonly used in natural language processing tasks, particularly for evaluating nested named entity recognition models.

properties.name: 宏平均F1
properties.description: 宏平均F1是一种评估指标，用于衡量分类模型的性能，特别是在多类别分类任务中。它通过计算每个类别的F1分数的平均值来评估模型的整体性能，不考虑类别样本数量的不平衡。

properties.name: 微平均F1
properties.description: 微平均F1是一种评估指标，用于衡量跨语言命名实体识别模型的整体性能，通过计算所有类别的精确率和召回率的调和平均数来评估模型的表现。

properties.name: CoNLL-2002
properties.description: A dataset for named entity recognition tasks, specifically focusing on cross-language named entity recognition.

properties.name: WikiAnn
properties.description: A multilingual named entity recognition dataset derived from Wikipedia articles, covering multiple languages and entity types.

properties.name: XNLI
properties.description: Cross-lingual Natural Language Inference dataset used for evaluating cross-lingual understanding in natural language processing tasks.

properties.name: X-WikiNER
properties.description: A dataset for cross-lingual named entity recognition, commonly used in natural language processing tasks.

properties.name: MultiCoNER
properties.description: A dataset for multilingual and cross-lingual named entity recognition tasks.

properties.name: Accuracy
properties.description: A metric that measures the proportion of correctly identified named entities out of all predicted named entities in a fine-grained named entity recognition task.

properties.name: Micro-F1
properties.description: A metric that calculates the F1 score by considering the overall precision and recall across all classes, giving equal weight to each instance in the dataset.

properties.name: Macro-F1
properties.description: Macro-F1 is the unweighted mean of F1 scores across all classes, treating all classes equally regardless of their frequency.

properties.name: FIGER
properties.description: A dataset for fine-grained named entity recognition, providing annotations for a wide range of entity types.

properties.name: BBN
properties.description: A dataset used for fine-grained named entity recognition in natural language processing.

properties.name: WikiFNE
properties.description: A dataset for fine-grained named entity recognition, derived from Wikipedia articles.

properties.name: 分词

properties.applications: 搜索引擎、机器翻译、语音识别、文本分析

properties.name: 组块分析
properties.description: 组块分析是自然语言处理中的一项任务，旨在识别文本中的短语或组块，如名词短语、动词短语等，而不深入分析其内部结构。
properties.applications: 信息提取、句法分析、机器翻译

properties.name: BLEU
properties.description: A metric for evaluating the quality of machine-translated text by comparing it to reference translations using n-gram precision and a brevity penalty.

properties.name: NIST
properties.description: A method for evaluating the quality of machine translation output that considers the importance of words based on their frequency in a reference corpus.
properties.range: 0 to positive infinity, where higher scores indicate better translation quality

properties.name: TER
properties.description: Translation Edit Rate (TER) is a metric for evaluating the quality of machine translation output by measuring the number of edits required to change the machine-generated translation into a human reference translation.
properties.range: 0 to positive infinity (lower values indicate better translation quality)

properties.name: METEOR
properties.description: METEOR (Metric for Evaluation of Translation with Explicit ORdering) is a metric for evaluating machine translation output based on the harmonic mean of unigram precision and recall, with recall weighted higher than precision. It also includes measures for stemming, synonymy, and word order.

properties.name: Europarl
properties.description: A parallel corpus extracted from the proceedings of the European Parliament, widely used for statistical machine translation research and development.

properties.name: Hansards
properties.description: A bilingual corpus of Canadian parliamentary proceedings, commonly used in statistical machine translation research.

properties.name: United Nations Parallel Corpus

properties.name: WMT Shared Task Datasets

properties.name: chrF
properties.description: A metric for evaluating machine translation output by comparing character n-gram overlap between the hypothesis and reference texts.

properties.name: WMT

properties.name: IWSLT

properties.name: TED Talks

properties.name: OpenSubtitles

properties.name: DGT-TM

properties.name: UN Parallel Corpus

properties.name: ChrF
properties.description: ChrF is a metric for evaluating machine translation output by comparing character n-gram matches between the hypothesis and reference texts.

properties.name: COMET

properties.name: OPUS

properties.name: Multi30k

properties.name: Flores

properties.name: EMEA

properties.name: UN Corpus

properties.name: Bible Corpus

properties.name: WOZ 2.0
properties.description: A dataset for dialogue state tracking in task-oriented dialogue systems, collected using the Wizard of Oz method.

properties.name: Schema-Guided Dialogue
properties.description: A dataset designed for task-oriented dialogue systems, providing schemas to guide the dialogue state tracking and natural language understanding processes.

properties.name: CrossWOZ
properties.description: A large-scale cross-domain Chinese task-oriented dialogue dataset for dialogue state tracking and other dialogue-related tasks.

properties.name: 对话成功率
properties.description: 衡量对话系统成功完成预定对话目标的比例，通常以百分比表示

properties.name: 平均对话轮数
properties.description: 衡量对话系统中完成一次完整对话所需的平均轮数，用于评估对话策略的效率

properties.name: 用户满意度评分
properties.description: 用于评估问答系统中对话管理策略优化效果的指标，反映用户对系统交互体验的满意程度

properties.name: 任务完成率
properties.description: 衡量对话系统成功完成用户指定任务的比例，是评估对话策略优化效果的核心指标

properties.name: 错误恢复率
properties.description: 衡量对话系统在出现错误后能够成功恢复对话的能力的指标

properties.name: Taskmaster-1
properties.description: A dataset designed for dialogue management and dialogue strategy optimization in question answering systems, featuring multi-turn conversations.

properties.name: 对话连贯性评分
properties.description: 用于评估多轮对话中对话内容的连贯性和逻辑性的指标

properties.name: 上下文相关性得分
properties.description: 用于评估多轮对话中系统响应与对话历史上下文的关联程度的指标

properties.name: 对话轮次效率
properties.description: 衡量多轮对话系统中完成特定任务所需对话轮次的效率指标，通常以完成任务所需的最少轮次与实际轮次的比值计算

properties.name: DSTC
properties.description: Dialog State Tracking Challenge dataset for multi-turn dialogue understanding

properties.name: DialoGLUE
properties.description: A benchmark dataset for evaluating dialogue understanding systems, focusing on multi-turn dialogue comprehension tasks.

properties.name: Clinc150
properties.description: A dataset designed for intent classification in task-oriented dialogue systems, containing 150 intent classes across 10 domains.

properties.name: 上下文连贯性
properties.description: 评估对话或文本中上下文之间逻辑和语义连贯性的指标

properties.name: 对话历史准确率
properties.description: 衡量对话系统在理解和利用对话历史上下文方面的准确程度，通常通过比较系统对历史对话内容的处理与预期结果的一致性来评估。

properties.name: ConvAI2
properties.description: A dataset for training and evaluating conversational AI models, focusing on persona-based dialogues and context-aware responses.

properties.name: Persona-Chat
properties.description: A dataset designed for training and evaluating dialogue models in the context of persona-based conversations, where each participant has a consistent profile.

properties.name: DUC 2005
properties.description: A dataset used for query-oriented summarization tasks in natural language processing, particularly in the context of graph-based summarization.

properties.name: DUC 2006
properties.description: A dataset used for query-oriented summarization tasks in natural language processing, particularly in the context of graph-based summarization approaches.

properties.name: TREC 2007 QA
properties.description: A dataset used for query-oriented summarization in the Text REtrieval Conference (TREC) 2007, focusing on question answering tasks.

properties.name: DialogSum
properties.description: A large-scale dialogue summarization dataset for text summarization tasks, focusing on summarizing conversations.

properties.name: MediaSum
properties.description: A large-scale media interview dataset for dialogue summarization

properties.name: SummScreen
properties.description: A dataset for dialogue summarization, focusing on summarizing TV show transcripts into concise summaries.

properties.name: TODSum
properties.description: A dataset for task-oriented dialogue summarization, designed to facilitate research in summarizing multi-turn dialogues with specific goals or tasks.

properties.name: arXiv
properties.description: A free distribution service and open-access archive for scholarly articles in the fields of physics, mathematics, computer science, quantitative biology, quantitative finance, statistics, electrical engineering and systems science, and economics.

properties.name: ScienceDirect
properties.description: A leading full-text scientific database offering journal articles and book chapters from more than 2,500 peer-reviewed journals and more than 11,000 books.

properties.name: Scopus
properties.description: A comprehensive bibliographic database containing abstracts and citations for academic journal articles in the fields of science, technology, medicine, social sciences, and arts and humanities.

properties.name: Web of Science
properties.description: A comprehensive research database providing access to multidisciplinary literature from scholarly journals, books, and conference proceedings.

properties.name: DUC 2007
properties.description: A dataset used for query-focused summarization tasks in natural language processing, part of the Document Understanding Conferences (DUC) series.

properties.name: TAC 2009
properties.description: A dataset used for query-focused summarization tasks in natural language processing, part of the Text Analysis Conference series.

properties.name: 微观平均F1
properties.description: 一种评估指标，用于衡量实体消歧任务中所有类别的整体性能，通过计算所有样本的F1分数的平均值得到

properties.name: macro-average F1
properties.description: A metric that calculates the F1 score for each class independently and then takes the average (treating all classes equally), used to evaluate the performance of entity disambiguation systems.

properties.name: AIDA-CoNLL
properties.description: A dataset for named entity recognition and disambiguation, commonly used for evaluating entity linking systems.

properties.name: ACE
properties.description: Automatic Content Extraction dataset, a standard corpus for entity linking and disambiguation tasks in natural language processing
